715673f-a.title: Manhattan: 153rd Street (West) - 7th Avenue
715673f-a.text:
(1)
West 153rd Street, west from, but not including Seventh, to and includ-
ing Edgecombe Aves. The view shows the rear of billboards, which are on the
east side of Maconmbs Place, from mest 153rd to 152nd Streets.
August 29, 1935.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUO IONS.
(2)
The same, from a different angle, and including a portion of Harlem
Lane Park, on the right.
August 29, 1935.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
